      "value": "Fallbrook Union High is a small high school district in the North Inland region of San Diego County. About 317 of its students have an IEP, and 34 of them \u2014 roughly 11% \u2014 have an autism (ASD) eligibility. Around 44% of those autistic students spend most of the school day in a general-education classroom."
    },
